      • onSubmit

        void onSubmit(AbstractForm.SubmitEvent event)
        Fired when the form is submitted.

        The AbstractForm must not be detached (i.e. removed from its parent or otherwise disconnected from a RootPanel) until the submission is complete. Otherwise, notification of submission will fail.

        Parameters:
        event - the event
